## AssembledFeature.eventHandlerName property

The name of the event handler. A naming convention is `onDOM` + PascalCase event name, to avoid any collision with WebView's own props.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
readonly eventHandlerName: E;
```

## Example

onDOMLinkPress
